n\r\nand then gone:\r\n\r\n```\r\nETH: LES: Send: [ LES,     GetTxStatus ]\r\nETH: SEND: L  2: [\r\nETH: SEND:   I  1: 0x24\r\nETH: SEND:   L  2: [\r\nETH: SEND:     I  1: 0x05\r\nETH: SEND:     L  1: [\r\nETH: SEND:       I 32: 0x9ff747c87e646fdf1e47df3954b8205e404a47b456fac5e46cf5da21fc128a64\r\nETH: SEND:     ]\r\nETH: SEND:   ]\r\nETH: SEND: ]\r\nETH: RECV: L  3: [\r\nETH: RECV:   I  1: 0x05\r\nETH: RECV:   I  4: 0x11e1a300\r\nETH: RECV:   L  1: [\r\nETH: RECV:     L  3: [\r\nETH: RECV:       I  0: 0x\r\nETH: RECV:       L  0: []\r\nETH: RECV:       I  0: 0x\r\nETH: RECV:     ]\r\nETH: RECV:   ]\r\nETH: RECV: ]\r\nETH: LES: Recv: [ LES,        TxStatus ] \r\n```\r\nWhy is there no 'error' status?",
